# ArgLib Server

Thin FastAPI service that exposes ArgLib graph CRUD, mining, diagnostics, and export endpoints.

## Goals
- Serve as the backend for arglib-ui.
- Keep all core logic inside the arglib library.
- Provide a stable API contract (OpenAPI).

## Quick start (planned)
- `uv sync`
- `uv run arglib-server`

## Notes
This is a scaffold with in-memory storage only. Use for local development.

## API surface (initial)
- `POST /graphs` create
- `GET /graphs/{graph_id}` fetch
- `PUT /graphs/{graph_id}` update
- `DELETE /graphs/{graph_id}` delete
- `POST /graphs/{graph_id}/diagnostics`
- `POST /graphs/{graph_id}/credibility`
- `POST /graphs/{graph_id}/export`
- `POST /mining/parse`

OpenAPI spec lives at `openapi.yaml`.
